thread.title_full: Better Music reviewed by Sam from Victoria

author: Sam from Victoria
title: Sam from Victoria
text: I ordered online from Victoria, I was super happy they had what I needed in Stock, none of the stores in vic had it in Stock. I asked for express shipping, they range 30 minutes after I placed my order to check all my shipping info, and it was on the truck the very next day, and was on my door step the following day. Two days! I can't express how happy I am with that!
